{"tid":9332,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲打好鍾意唱歌但係好難聽","createTime":"2016-11-28T14:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:05:52.000Z","uid":12467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8482ecab91fb4a0fee573abb8350e1bd42d7721","tid":9332,"uid":12467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"音域超細<br />\n上唔到高音假音<br />\n呢排上youtube睇人教唱歌<br />\n諗住有d進步啦<br />\n點知自己用iphone錄音聽下<br />\n先發覺自己把聲咁小學雞咁滑稽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明平時聽到自己把聲係好深情好憂鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為自己好適合唱d失戀叫春歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ff5e853ce58ebec0db978e88b1b75d056b1a12","tid":9332,"uid":12467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e58cf7a575e549c881f5699651c92548887267","tid":9332,"uid":10457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"自己勁中意聽啲又厚又沙聲既歌手<br />\n<br />\n自己一唱發覺把聲勁薄 不過都要繼續唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713d392e2912d0c66f61be7473aad34c6e08d2f0","tid":9332,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲係家族遺傳，<br />\n真係一句：好講天份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我全家唱歌都唱唔到高音，<br />\n直情去到好多歌副歌位唱都唱唔到（一係走音）<br />\n可以話好多歌都唱唔哂一首，<br />\n以前細個去唱k仲諗住唱得多會好，<br />\n但事實係唱幾多年都係咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.s.好羨慕人地鳩唱都可以唱哂成首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3a285d30a09f605293460a55f0f89988441c2b","tid":9332,"uid":14961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:32:11.000Z","msg"